WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:24.983 --> 00:00:31.364 position:50% align:center
[car approaches]

00:00:38.955 --> 00:00:40.540 position:50% align:center
[horn honks]

00:01:13.656 --> 00:01:15.450 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Ai Ohto.

00:01:20.580 --> 00:01:22.874 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] What are you
doing in a place like this?

00:01:24.584 --> 00:01:26.503 position:50% align:center
Walking.

00:01:26.586 --> 00:01:28.880 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
This late at night?

00:01:28.963 --> 00:01:30.173 position:50% align:center
Uh?!

00:01:30.256 --> 00:01:32.342 position:50% align:center
A dream?

00:01:32.425 --> 00:01:33.968 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
You don't like dreams?

00:01:34.052 --> 00:01:36.680 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Perhaps you prefer reality.

00:01:39.557 --> 00:01:41.476 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
The first time's free.

00:01:41.559 --> 00:01:43.436 position:50% align:center
After that, bring your wallet.

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:44.646 position:50% align:center
[AI]
How much?

00:01:44.729 --> 00:01:46.940 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] Don't worry.
I know you'll like it.

00:01:47.023 --> 00:01:50.527 position:50% align:center
It's for a very a special
capsule machine.

00:01:50.610 --> 00:01:53.029 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Special how?

00:01:53.113 --> 00:01:55.448 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
It has the thing you want in it.

00:01:55.532 --> 00:01:59.661 position:50% align:center
[AI] Okay, but there isn't
really anything I want.

00:02:06.334 --> 00:02:10.672 position:50% align:center
[ACCAS laugh]

00:02:10.755 --> 00:02:13.717 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Don't lie! Of course there is.

00:02:16.219 --> 00:02:17.637 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Huh

00:02:18.555 --> 00:02:20.849 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Like a friend.

00:02:45.457 --> 00:02:47.542 position:50% align:center
[AI]
It wasn't a dream.

00:02:48.835 --> 00:02:51.755 position:50% align:center
[AI] Should I refrigerate it
or something?

00:02:53.214 --> 00:02:57.510 position:50% align:center
[AI] Wait. It's an egg,
so maybe I should sit on it.

00:02:59.095 --> 00:03:01.181 position:50% align:center
It's hard.

00:03:02.223 --> 00:03:04.893 position:50% align:center
Hmm...

00:03:04.976 --> 00:03:09.356 position:50% align:center
Oh. What if I boil
the egg by accident?

00:03:09.439 --> 00:03:11.441 position:50% align:center
Can I crack it?

00:03:11.524 --> 00:03:15.528 position:50% align:center
Actually, I'm not even sure
if I should crack the thing.

00:03:19.282 --> 00:03:20.408 position:50% align:center
[STUDENTS laughing]

00:03:20.492 --> 00:03:21.576 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT A]
I gotta drop off my bag first,

00:03:21.659 --> 00:03:23.745 position:50% align:center
wanna just meet there?

00:03:23.828 --> 00:03:25.080 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT B]
The usual place?

00:03:25.163 --> 00:03:26.373 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT A]
Yep!

00:03:26.915 --> 00:03:29.834 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
Ai? Your teacher is here.

00:03:29.918 --> 00:03:32.921 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI] Oh, there's no need
to force her to get up, ma'am.

00:03:33.004 --> 00:03:35.924 position:50% align:center
I just wanted to bring
her this week's printouts.

00:03:36.007 --> 00:03:37.133 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
I'm so sorry.

00:03:37.217 --> 00:03:39.344 position:50% align:center
Thank you for being so kind.

00:03:39.427 --> 00:03:41.096 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
Please, it's nothing.

00:03:41.179 --> 00:03:42.472 position:50% align:center
You're on my way home...

00:03:42.555 --> 00:03:44.891 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I wonder what's in it.

00:03:44.974 --> 00:03:47.560 position:50% align:center
I'll try going back
there tomorrow.

00:03:51.606 --> 00:03:53.191 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:04:06.496 --> 00:04:08.164 position:50% align:center
[AI whispers]
I'm going out.

00:04:16.381 --> 00:04:18.008 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:04:20.093 --> 00:04:22.429 position:50% align:center
Whoa, crazy.

00:04:31.104 --> 00:04:34.315 position:50% align:center
[AI]
How'd I get to my school?

00:04:36.401 --> 00:04:38.319 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT C]
You're overdoing it.

00:04:38.403 --> 00:04:40.655 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT D] If I don't,
she won't get the message, duh.

00:04:40.739 --> 00:04:42.615 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT C]
In that case, check this out.

00:04:42.699 --> 00:04:45.285 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT D]
Whoa, brutal! I love it.

00:04:48.997 --> 00:04:51.332 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:04:51.416 --> 00:04:52.542 position:50% align:center
Ah!

00:04:52.625 --> 00:04:54.085 position:50% align:center
[INOUE] For those of
you at school today,

00:04:54.169 --> 00:04:56.171 position:50% align:center
I pose this question:

00:04:56.254 --> 00:04:57.464 position:50% align:center
What do you think you should do

00:04:57.547 --> 00:05:00.300 position:50% align:center
if someone else in
your class is being bullied?

00:05:00.383 --> 00:05:02.010 position:50% align:center
Ding, ding! Correct!

00:05:02.093 --> 00:05:04.137 position:50% align:center
You pretend not to see it!

00:05:04.220 --> 00:05:07.349 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:05:11.644 --> 00:05:12.979 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:05:22.489 --> 00:05:23.698 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:05:26.451 --> 00:05:28.036 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Ai Ohto.

00:05:29.704 --> 00:05:31.164 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Just break it.

00:05:31.247 --> 00:05:33.375 position:50% align:center
What are you waiting for?

00:05:33.458 --> 00:05:34.501 position:50% align:center
Break what?

00:05:34.584 --> 00:05:35.794 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
The Wonder Egg.

00:05:38.254 --> 00:05:39.506 position:50% align:center
You mean this?

00:05:39.589 --> 00:05:41.633 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Yes, break it.

00:05:41.716 --> 00:05:44.511 position:50% align:center
But... it's way
too hard for me to crack.

00:05:44.594 --> 00:05:46.513 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Enough talking!

00:05:46.596 --> 00:05:49.641 position:50% align:center
Break it! Break the egg!

00:05:51.476 --> 00:05:52.560 position:50% align:center
Shut up!

00:05:52.644 --> 00:05:54.145 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA laughs]

00:05:54.229 --> 00:05:56.481 position:50% align:center
That's the spirit.

00:06:02.904 --> 00:06:04.197 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:06:30.974 --> 00:06:32.642 position:50% align:center
[yelps]

00:06:36.938 --> 00:06:41.234 position:50% align:center
[running sink]

00:06:41.317 --> 00:06:43.153 position:50% align:center
[KURUMI] Damn, why'd
you have to break the egg

00:06:43.236 --> 00:06:45.572 position:50% align:center
in a dumb bathroom?

00:06:48.491 --> 00:06:50.076 position:50% align:center
If you're done, leave.

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:51.453 position:50% align:center
[AI]
'Kay.

00:06:54.956 --> 00:06:57.042 position:50% align:center
[AI]
She didn't have to be so rude.

00:06:57.125 --> 00:07:01.171 position:50% align:center
Her attitude sucks.
Just ask nicely.

00:07:01.254 --> 00:07:03.631 position:50% align:center
But, still, I left.

00:07:03.715 --> 00:07:10.263 position:50% align:center
♪ march-style music playing ♪

00:07:10.347 --> 00:07:11.765 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Huh?

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:20.273 position:50% align:center
Stand up!

00:07:20.357 --> 00:07:21.399 position:50% align:center
Right!

00:07:21.483 --> 00:07:22.942 position:50% align:center
--[KURUMI] Let's run.
--Huh?

00:07:28.448 --> 00:07:30.158 position:50% align:center
What's happening?

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:37.499 position:50% align:center
--Uh, are you okay?
--[KURUMI] We need to run.

00:07:37.582 --> 00:07:44.130 position:50% align:center
[eerie laughter]

00:07:46.591 --> 00:07:48.510 position:50% align:center
What are they?

00:07:48.593 --> 00:07:50.345 position:50% align:center
[KURUMI]
You should know!

00:07:51.346 --> 00:07:53.306 position:50% align:center
They're Seeno Evils!

00:07:53.390 --> 00:07:54.849 position:50% align:center
[AI]
What's that?

00:07:54.933 --> 00:07:56.601 position:50% align:center
[KURUMI]
No idea!

00:08:02.399 --> 00:08:05.193 position:50% align:center
[KURUMI]
Come on! Quick, this way!

00:08:05.276 --> 00:08:07.112 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Wait for me!

00:08:21.751 --> 00:08:23.336 position:50% align:center
[AI whimpers]

00:08:23.420 --> 00:08:25.213 position:50% align:center
Is this where my liver is?

00:08:25.296 --> 00:08:26.881 position:50% align:center
Am I going to die?

00:08:28.633 --> 00:08:30.218 position:50% align:center
Let's go.

00:08:46.985 --> 00:08:48.570 position:50% align:center
Run faster!

00:08:57.662 --> 00:08:58.830 position:50% align:center
It's a dream.

00:08:58.913 --> 00:09:00.582 position:50% align:center
Like a nightmare, right?

00:09:00.665 --> 00:09:02.917 position:50% align:center
Show me your wound.

00:09:03.001 --> 00:09:03.752 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:09:03.835 --> 00:09:05.503 position:50% align:center
Hurry up.

00:09:08.089 --> 00:09:10.342 position:50% align:center
It's gone?

00:09:10.425 --> 00:09:13.636 position:50% align:center
My wounds don't disappear.

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:19.309 position:50% align:center
This is a dream to you, but for
someone like me, it's reality.

00:09:19.392 --> 00:09:20.518 position:50% align:center
Here's the plan.

00:09:20.602 --> 00:09:23.355 position:50% align:center
We run until the bell rings.

00:09:23.438 --> 00:09:25.231 position:50% align:center
Hey, don't be
such a scaredy cat.

00:09:25.315 --> 00:09:28.151 position:50% align:center
The good news is those
things are only after me.

00:09:28.234 --> 00:09:31.029 position:50% align:center
And you're immortal
in this world, lucky duck.

00:09:31.112 --> 00:09:33.990 position:50% align:center
Well, as long as
your eyes and heart are okay.

00:09:34.074 --> 00:09:36.493 position:50% align:center
Wait, how does
that qualify as immortal?

00:09:36.576 --> 00:09:38.578 position:50% align:center
True. My bad.

00:09:39.579 --> 00:09:40.997 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Why is this happening to me?

00:09:41.081 --> 00:09:42.582 position:50% align:center
Because you bought the Egg, duh.

00:09:42.665 --> 00:09:43.833 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I did not.

00:09:43.917 --> 00:09:45.960 position:50% align:center
They said the
first one was free.

00:09:46.044 --> 00:09:47.128 position:50% align:center
[KURUMI]
Yeah?

00:09:47.212 --> 00:09:50.131 position:50% align:center
Nothing costs more
than a free gift, huh?

00:09:50.215 --> 00:09:51.424 position:50% align:center
It's not funny.

00:09:51.508 --> 00:09:53.259 position:50% align:center
So, you've got no friends?

00:09:53.343 --> 00:09:54.761 position:50% align:center
[AI]
It's not like that.

00:09:54.844 --> 00:09:56.846 position:50% align:center
I just don't need them.

00:09:56.930 --> 00:09:58.390 position:50% align:center
Suuuure.

00:09:58.473 --> 00:09:59.891 position:50% align:center
[AI]
It's true.

00:09:59.974 --> 00:10:03.395 position:50% align:center
Yeah, right, you wouldn't
have broken the Egg if it were.

00:10:03.478 --> 00:10:06.356 position:50% align:center
It's nothing to be ashamed of.

00:10:06.439 --> 00:10:07.565 position:50% align:center
I didn't have any either.

00:10:07.649 --> 00:10:08.525 position:50% align:center
Sure.

00:10:08.608 --> 00:10:10.318 position:50% align:center
[KURUMI]
I'm serious.

00:10:10.402 --> 00:10:12.987 position:50% align:center
Well, I guess
I had the fake kind.

00:10:13.071 --> 00:10:14.698 position:50% align:center
You know, the ones
that are all like,

00:10:14.781 --> 00:10:18.451 position:50% align:center
"Totally!" and "OMG, so funny!"

00:10:20.245 --> 00:10:23.081 position:50% align:center
But I didn't have a best friend.

00:10:23.164 --> 00:10:26.876 position:50% align:center
Thinking back on it,
best friends are important.

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.211 position:50% align:center
You break up with boyfriends,

00:10:28.294 --> 00:10:30.714 position:50% align:center
but best friends
are forever, right?

00:10:30.797 --> 00:10:33.550 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I guess.

00:10:33.633 --> 00:10:35.343 position:50% align:center
You had a boyfriend?

00:10:35.427 --> 00:10:36.594 position:50% align:center
Did you?

00:10:36.678 --> 00:10:39.014 position:50% align:center
Pretty sure I asked you first.

00:10:39.097 --> 00:10:41.266 position:50% align:center
Fine. We'll say on "go."

00:10:41.349 --> 00:10:44.185 position:50% align:center
Okay.

00:10:44.269 --> 00:10:46.104 position:50% align:center
--[KURUMI] And "go."
--[AI] And "go."

00:10:48.815 --> 00:10:49.858 position:50% align:center
You cheater!

00:10:49.941 --> 00:10:52.110 position:50% align:center
Says the cheater!

00:10:52.861 --> 00:10:54.529 position:50% align:center
Hey.

00:10:58.783 --> 00:11:00.535 position:50% align:center
Let's go.

00:11:12.297 --> 00:11:13.631 position:50% align:center
Sorry.

00:11:13.715 --> 00:11:16.426 position:50% align:center
Don't be sorry.

00:11:16.509 --> 00:11:18.803 position:50% align:center
Besides, this is their fault.

00:11:20.472 --> 00:11:22.390 position:50% align:center
Sorry!

00:11:26.644 --> 00:11:29.981 position:50% align:center
[AI] It's true.
They don't care about me.

00:11:31.107 --> 00:11:35.070 position:50% align:center
[AI]
They don't... attack me.

00:12:36.006 --> 00:12:37.549 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Koito?

00:12:44.889 --> 00:12:47.767 position:50% align:center
[AI sobs]

00:12:47.851 --> 00:12:49.728 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
I'm Koito Nagase.

00:12:49.811 --> 00:12:52.272 position:50% align:center
I really hope that
we can all be friends.

00:12:52.355 --> 00:12:53.356 position:50% align:center
[TEACHER]
Thank you, Nagase.

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:56.192 position:50% align:center
Please take
the seat next to Ohto.

00:12:56.276 --> 00:12:57.652 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Right.

00:13:18.715 --> 00:13:20.842 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Wanna walk together?

00:13:22.093 --> 00:13:23.011 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
C'mon.

00:13:23.094 --> 00:13:24.763 position:50% align:center
Don't act so confused.

00:13:24.846 --> 00:13:25.972 position:50% align:center
It'll be fun.

00:13:29.809 --> 00:13:33.146 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Oh, wow. It's quiet out here.

00:13:35.440 --> 00:13:36.900 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
What's that?

00:13:36.983 --> 00:13:38.443 position:50% align:center
Game.

00:13:38.526 --> 00:13:40.487 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
You like games?

00:13:40.570 --> 00:13:42.072 position:50% align:center
I guess.

00:13:42.155 --> 00:13:43.698 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Hmm...

00:13:43.782 --> 00:13:45.367 position:50% align:center
What kind?

00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:50.413 position:50% align:center
What's the matter?

00:13:50.497 --> 00:13:52.916 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Look... Um...

00:13:52.999 --> 00:13:56.544 position:50% align:center
I don't think you should hang
out with me, it's a bad idea.

00:13:56.628 --> 00:13:57.837 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Why's that?

00:13:57.921 --> 00:14:00.548 position:50% align:center
It's 'cause I'm ugly.

00:14:03.343 --> 00:14:04.511 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
What?

00:14:04.594 --> 00:14:06.680 position:50% align:center
You're not even a little ugly.

00:14:06.763 --> 00:14:09.224 position:50% align:center
You've got big,
pretty, round eyes.

00:14:09.307 --> 00:14:11.685 position:50% align:center
But with your bangs.

00:14:11.768 --> 00:14:13.728 position:50% align:center
Why do you hide this eye?

00:14:22.487 --> 00:14:23.988 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
Where's your umbrella?

00:14:24.072 --> 00:14:25.407 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I forgot it.

00:14:25.490 --> 00:14:29.828 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
And your bag? Ai?

00:14:29.911 --> 00:14:32.288 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I forgot it.

00:14:32.372 --> 00:14:33.540 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
Is something wrong?

00:14:33.623 --> 00:14:36.167 position:50% align:center
[AI]
No, I'm fine!

00:14:47.470 --> 00:14:50.348 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
Ai! A friend is here to see you.

00:14:50.432 --> 00:14:52.308 position:50% align:center
[AI]
She's not my friend.

00:14:52.392 --> 00:14:54.227 position:50% align:center
I don't have friends.

00:15:05.530 --> 00:15:09.451 position:50% align:center
You forgot your stuff,
so I brought it over.

00:15:09.534 --> 00:15:11.661 position:50% align:center
Thanks a lot.

00:15:19.711 --> 00:15:21.963 position:50% align:center
[KOITO] That's called
heterochromia, right?

00:15:22.047 --> 00:15:23.798 position:50% align:center
When your eyes
are different colors?

00:15:23.882 --> 00:15:26.718 position:50% align:center
Animals have it. Yeah.

00:15:26.801 --> 00:15:28.720 position:50% align:center
It's mysterious.

00:15:28.803 --> 00:15:30.597 position:50% align:center
You shouldn't try to hide it.

00:15:31.806 --> 00:15:35.185 position:50% align:center
[yawns]

00:15:41.066 --> 00:15:44.694 position:50% align:center
I get bullied for it. A lot.

00:15:54.454 --> 00:15:57.374 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
It's pretty.

00:16:07.092 --> 00:16:10.095 position:50% align:center
I want you to be
friends with me.

00:16:13.348 --> 00:16:16.976 position:50% align:center
In fact, let's be best friends.

00:16:17.060 --> 00:16:19.604 position:50% align:center
Want to?

00:16:19.688 --> 00:16:22.816 position:50% align:center
I guess I'd like to, but...

00:16:22.899 --> 00:16:25.443 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
But?

00:16:25.527 --> 00:16:28.863 position:50% align:center
If we could, I'd be happy.

00:16:29.698 --> 00:16:31.574 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Me, too.

00:16:32.784 --> 00:16:35.495 position:50% align:center
[AI]
It's all my fault.

00:16:35.578 --> 00:16:40.166 position:50% align:center
Because I betrayed you.

00:16:40.250 --> 00:16:44.129 position:50% align:center
Even though you were
the first friend I ever made.

00:16:45.588 --> 00:16:47.215 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:16:53.471 --> 00:16:55.557 position:50% align:center
Are you crying?

00:17:03.064 --> 00:17:10.447 position:50% align:center
[clapping]

00:17:15.035 --> 00:17:21.833 position:50% align:center
[INOUE laughing]

00:17:21.916 --> 00:17:22.959 position:50% align:center
I'm so close.

00:17:23.043 --> 00:17:25.837 position:50% align:center
I just have to make it
a little longer!

00:17:28.381 --> 00:17:30.425 position:50% align:center
I'm sick of this.

00:17:35.889 --> 00:17:37.265 position:50% align:center
Stay away from me!

00:17:48.735 --> 00:17:50.278 position:50% align:center
Crosswalks are still scary.

00:17:50.362 --> 00:17:52.405 position:50% align:center
Even when you move
with the crowd.

00:17:52.489 --> 00:17:53.948 position:50% align:center
It doesn't matter.

00:17:54.032 --> 00:17:57.452 position:50% align:center
So, I'm done with pretending
that I don't see anything!

00:18:07.587 --> 00:18:16.471 position:50% align:center
[INOUE laughing]

00:18:22.435 --> 00:18:26.815 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:18:26.898 --> 00:18:29.609 position:50% align:center
Ha ha ha... Huh?

00:18:29.693 --> 00:18:33.530 position:50% align:center
Now, I'm really angry!

00:18:33.613 --> 00:18:34.781 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:18:45.834 --> 00:18:56.136 position:50% align:center
♪ march-style music playing ♪

00:18:56.219 --> 00:18:58.263 position:50% align:center
[KURUMI]
I'm Kurumi Saijo.

00:18:58.346 --> 00:18:59.931 position:50% align:center
Ai Ohto.

00:19:00.015 --> 00:19:02.934 position:50% align:center
Well, Ai, this is goodbye.

00:19:03.018 --> 00:19:04.477 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:19:05.812 --> 00:19:07.188 position:50% align:center
Thanks for your help.

00:19:07.272 --> 00:19:09.065 position:50% align:center
Don't forget me.

00:19:11.818 --> 00:19:13.111 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Too bad.

00:19:13.194 --> 00:19:14.529 position:50% align:center
Only you get saved.

00:19:14.612 --> 00:19:17.198 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
But you have to cheer up.

00:19:17.282 --> 00:19:19.993 position:50% align:center
If you want your
best friend back.

00:19:20.076 --> 00:19:21.578 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Hmm?

00:19:24.789 --> 00:19:26.833 position:50% align:center
[AI]
She's a little warm.

00:19:26.916 --> 00:19:30.378 position:50% align:center
Is it because I saved Kurumi?

00:19:30.462 --> 00:19:32.630 position:50% align:center
Hey. If I save more people,

00:19:32.714 --> 00:19:35.592 position:50% align:center
then, will Koito come back?

00:19:35.675 --> 00:19:37.260 position:50% align:center
Tell me she will!

00:19:40.055 --> 00:19:42.349 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
Ai! Breakfast!

00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:48.897 position:50% align:center
Thanks for the food.

00:19:50.440 --> 00:19:51.983 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
The weather is beautiful today.

00:19:52.067 --> 00:19:54.903 position:50% align:center
Try not to waste it
lying around.

00:19:54.986 --> 00:19:56.071 position:50% align:center
I hung up the laundry to dry,

00:19:56.154 --> 00:19:59.991 position:50% align:center
so can you bring it
in this afternoon?

00:20:00.075 --> 00:20:04.746 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Oh, I'm immortal there, but...

00:20:07.290 --> 00:20:08.291 position:50% align:center
For lunch...

00:20:08.375 --> 00:20:10.126 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:12.128 --> 00:20:13.505 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
What happened?

00:20:13.588 --> 00:20:16.424 position:50% align:center
[TAE sobs]
I don't know. I have no idea!

00:20:16.508 --> 00:20:18.551 position:50% align:center
Maybe she snuck out last night
and did who knows what?

00:20:18.635 --> 00:20:20.887 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
It'll be all right.

00:20:20.970 --> 00:20:23.014 position:50% align:center
I'll save you.

00:20:42.117 --> 00:20:44.744 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Hi. How are your injuries?

00:20:44.828 --> 00:20:46.121 position:50% align:center
They're okay.

00:20:46.204 --> 00:20:47.497 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
And your wallet?

00:20:47.580 --> 00:20:49.874 position:50% align:center
Right here.

00:20:49.958 --> 00:20:52.043 position:50% align:center
How many rescues
do I need to save Koito?

00:20:52.127 --> 00:20:54.421 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Hm. I can't say.

00:20:54.504 --> 00:20:58.008 position:50% align:center
[AI] If I protect more at once,
will it bring her back faster?

00:20:58.091 --> 00:20:59.926 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
You're quite the greedy idiot.

00:21:00.010 --> 00:21:03.888 position:50% align:center
If you can't protect them,
then you won't make it, either.

00:21:05.306 --> 00:21:07.142 position:50% align:center
I have to try.

00:21:09.060 --> 00:21:12.063 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] You know your enemies
won't always be so easy, right?

00:21:12.147 --> 00:21:14.399 position:50% align:center
The Seeno Evils can be tough.

00:21:15.191 --> 00:21:17.485 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
What's a little mindless mob?

00:21:27.871 --> 00:21:29.622 position:50% align:center
[AI]
What happened to Kurumi?

00:21:29.706 --> 00:21:31.791 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA] She's a lot
like your best friend.

00:21:31.875 --> 00:21:33.501 position:50% align:center
A sculpture in some other world.

00:21:33.585 --> 00:21:35.211 position:50% align:center
And unless her friends
go to that world,

00:21:35.295 --> 00:21:38.840 position:50% align:center
she'll likely stay
that way forever.

00:21:38.923 --> 00:21:41.259 position:50% align:center
So, did she kill herself, too?

00:21:41.343 --> 00:21:42.802 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
No comment.

00:21:44.512 --> 00:21:46.848 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Yep, no comment!

00:22:03.907 --> 00:22:05.241 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Welcome.

00:22:07.160 --> 00:22:08.787 position:50% align:center
Nice to meet you.

00:22:08.870 --> 00:22:10.246 position:50% align:center
My name's Acca.

00:22:10.330 --> 00:22:14.250 position:50% align:center
And if you look over to your
left, you'll see Ura-Acca.

00:22:14.334 --> 00:22:15.377 position:50% align:center
Yo.

00:22:15.460 --> 00:22:16.419 position:50% align:center
Hi?

00:22:16.503 --> 00:22:17.587 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
There's someone ahead of you.

00:22:17.671 --> 00:22:19.214 position:50% align:center
You'll have to wait.

00:22:19.297 --> 00:22:20.382 position:50% align:center
'Kay.

00:22:23.134 --> 00:22:26.596 position:50% align:center
Uh. Wait, it's not just me?

00:22:36.564 --> 00:22:39.651 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Check it out. No way.

00:22:39.734 --> 00:22:41.820 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] Yes, we're
always worried about her.

00:22:41.903 --> 00:22:43.780 position:50% align:center
[AI]
She's so pretty!

00:22:43.863 --> 00:22:45.615 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Oh, that.

00:22:58.378 --> 00:23:00.046 position:50% align:center
[AI]
To be continued.